{"tid":1628970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"爭取蘇格蘭獨立 逾20萬人愛丁堡上街遊行      高喊「我們要什麼？獨立」等口號","createTime":"2019-10-06T05:41:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:51:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f7f00d5a5ab86ac334b57268647d7b3830cda6","tid":1628970,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"爭取蘇格蘭獨立 逾20萬人愛丁堡上街遊行<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-06<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕英國預定於數週內脫離歐洲聯盟，要求針對蘇格蘭脫離英國獨立再次舉行公投的呼聲高漲，主辦單位宣稱，超過20萬支持蘇格蘭獨立民眾今天在首府愛丁堡（Edinburgh）示威遊行。<br />\n<br />\n許多示威抗議者高舉蘇格蘭旗幟，部分民眾穿蘇格蘭短褶裙，一些人吹奏包括風笛等樂器，他們從市中心聖十字公園（Holyrood Park）出發，前往愛丁堡老城主要幹道皇家一英里（Royal Mile）。一些民眾沿途高喊「我們要什麼？獨立」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示威抗議群眾當中包括律師和蘇格蘭民族黨（SNP）國會議員柴里（Joanna Cherry），柴里是成功司法挑戰英國首相強生關閉國會舉措的主要推手之一。英國國會上個月通過一項法案，強制首相強生向歐盟要求更多時間，避免英國無協議脫歐，柴里也是法案的主要支持者之一。<br />\n<br />\n示威遊行主辦單位「團結在一面旗幟下」（All Under One Banner）宣稱，超過20萬人共襄盛舉，遠超出他們的預測。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭警方未提供估計參與人數。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭於2014年舉行獨立公投，結果55%選民反對獨立。但民族主義派人士主張，英國2016公投支持脫歐，意味蘇格蘭有必要再度舉行獨立公投，因為當年蘇格蘭有62%選民支持續留歐盟。<br />\n<br />\n蘇格蘭首席大臣同時也是蘇格蘭民族黨黨魁施特金（Nicola Sturgeon）堅稱，英國脫歐勢必會重創經濟。<br />\n<br />\n希望能於2021年舉辦第2次獨立公投的施特金無法參加今天的示威遊行，但她發推文表達支持。推文表示「別懷疑，獨立即將到臨」。<br />\n<br />\n一小撮挺英國民眾手持英國國旗，在愛丁堡市中心舉行反制示威抗議。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2937830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2937830&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=fdbceef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2937830&h=6eed2da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2937830</a>"},{"pid":"e778f7c6d7b0482a556a9bab96b49930a2ceff9a","tid":1628970,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6933ded49915d634d989d0c235d22693a42fa7d","tid":1628970,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4068e5bfd069dac5cf609c3a92fef62fadba8319","tid":1628970,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"今年成個世界都好撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"100a5c705163a0951fe152b153a5e494851f6649","tid":1628970,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"107f794e456b752083e656189b92f21e6d132c43","tid":1628970,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4068e5bfd069dac5cf609c3a92fef62fadba8319","tid":1628970,"uid":49853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"今年成個世界都好撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"WW3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c903f6e264a02e7b02b956cff7c875754992492b","tid":1628970,"uid":258192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ef21ba5d9b3f4af30186a3a2f86bf0983cce28","tid":1628970,"uid":267435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}